  "monster": {
    "title": "Jehaob.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Jehaob has a bug-like magenta body which hovers in mid-air and a cubic structure in place of a head.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 188     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++ ++++</lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +         </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: +..     </lightgrey><darkgrey>   rC: ...      </darkgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 140% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 84% to hit with your staff of alchemy and 82% to hit with your bite.\nIt has about 77% to hit you.\n\nAttack              Max Damage       \nHit: flaming touch  50 + 37 (flame)  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting the swamp drake.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
